Where did the data come from?

  • Academic, demographic, and disciplinary education data gathered from the 2014 - 2015 TN.gov.
  • Organized zipcodes by county Zip Codes.
  • Aggregated tax infomration organized by zipcode 2011 - 2015 IRS Data.
